# agent-delivery skill

## When to use

User mentions 想法/产品/架构/后端/前端/测试/交付, delivery gates, or product.yaml workflow.

## Steps

1. Load product root `AGENTS.md` and `product.yaml`.
2. Code-first by default; only enter delivery workflow when explicitly requested.
3. Validate with `ruby scripts/validate_workflow.rb` before changing delivery state.
4. Deliver with `ruby scripts/deliver.rb <task>`.
5. Keep product truths in the product repo; do not invent business rules in kit docs.
